// src/utils/chartSetup.js
import {
  Chart as ChartJS,
  CategoryScale,
  LinearScale,
  PointElement,
  LineElement,
  BarElement,
  ArcElement,
  Title,
  Tooltip,
  Legend
} from 'chart.js';

ChartJS.register(
  CategoryScale,
  LinearScale,
  PointElement,
  LineElement,
  BarElement,
  ArcElement,
  Title,
  Tooltip,
  Legend
);
